Package: gnome-remote-desktop
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         pipewire
Description: Remote desktop daemon for GNOME using pipewire
 This daemon enables GNOME to offer remote desktop sharing using VNC
 with Pipewire. It supports GNOME on X and GNOME on Wayland.
 .
 As long as mutter is configured correctly, this feature can be
 enabled in the GNOME Settings app.
